{"tid":531722,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"2月14號情人節，男人嘅惡夢，女人嘅綺夢","createTime":"2018-01-17T06:30:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T10:36:01.000Z","uid":12628,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"78414f26357619349e35f889ae9cbe523c42c016","tid":531722,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T06:30:21.000Z","msg":"屌你啦情人節，好地地一個日子港閪好多連呢個日子嘅出處未未知！人地華倫泰為情侶平權而犧牲，你班傻閪有個情人係身邊就應該滿足，要珍惜啦！你地又做過咩係呢個日子增進感情呀？有嘅，咪就係發白日夢同發脾氣囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但你班港閪比商家佬棍到啲港閪要人買野同做啲得別氹佢，唔做野就發嬲，做埋啲傻鳩野要博屌！<br />\n屌閪晒你地班撚閪，清明重陽唔見你班陷家剷咁上心？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仆街！閪痕就自慰啦8婆！男人做野好撚辛苦架，平日對你好咪算囉，又唔見你班港閪體諒下！智商你又無，情商你更加無，品行就差唔唔好提喇！<br />\n借情人節，我屌爆晒你班傻鳩港閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75f0ce525d8bb6eea24c97cb69a1ef8f91b683e","tid":531722,"uid":18568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T06:31:39.000Z","msg":"關我撚事咩<br />\n都係女"},{"pid":"995dd343805cd323de580a4d9ce76010491b3ef3","tid":531722,"uid":18568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T06:31:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關我撚事咩<br />\n都無女</blockquote>"},{"pid":"91e51e687d38a9684bc8a29688f0e8b1dbbb48b5","tid":531722,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T06:34:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關我撚事咩<br />\n都係女</blockquote><br />\n一齊屌港閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2dc81f1306bc8f0bde5e6cb035db6fc6782ad13","tid":531722,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T06:35:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9df3a82b2cd6f0b9ee4f6b00731e8590c6ce1fb1","tid":531722,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":